{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLSlotElement","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assign\"><code>assign()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedElements\"><code>assignedElements()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedNodes\"><code>assignedNodes()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/slotchange_event\"><code>slotchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Components</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/createElement\"><code>Document.createElement()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\"><code>Element.attachShadow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/shadowRoot\"><code>Element.shadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/slot\"><code>Element.slot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composed\"><code>Event.composed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>HTMLSlotElement</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">Shadow DOM API</a> enables access to the name and assigned nodes of an HTML <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> element.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlslotelement.name_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/name\"><code>HTMLSlotElement.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>: Can be used to get and set the slot's name.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlslotelement.assignednodes\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/assignedNodes\"><code>HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns the sequence of elements assigned to this slot, or alternatively the slot's fallback content.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following snippet is taken from our <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-components-examples/tree/master/slotchange\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">slotchange example</a> (<a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/web-components-examples/slotchange/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">see it live also</a>).</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> slots <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shadowRoot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'slot'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nslots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'slotchange'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> nodes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> slots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">assignedNodes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Element in Slot \"'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> slots<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\" changed to \"'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> nodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>outerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\".'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Here we grab references to all the slots, then add a slotchange event listener to the 2nd slot in the template — which is the one that keeps having its contents changed in the example.</p>\n\n<p>Every time the element inserted in the slot changes, we log a report to the console saying which slot has changed, and what the new node inside the slot is.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#htmlslotelement\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'HTMLSlotElement' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLSlotElement","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The HTMLSlotElement interface of the Shadow DOM API enables access to the name and assigned nodes of an HTML <slot> (en-US) element.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLSlotElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLSlotElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLSlotElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/htmlslotelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/htmlslotelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement","title":"HTMLSlotElement"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLSlotElement - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}